data.meta_description: President Franklin Delano Roosevelt and British Prime Minister Winston Churchill sightsee after completing conferences at Cairo and Tehran. Heads of State visit Pyramids and Sphinx.Roosevelt reviews troops at Camp Armibad. Statesman and President İsmet İnönü of Turkey in conference. With General Dwight David Eisenhower reviewing United States Army in Italy. FDR with sons Colonel Elliott Roosevelt and Lieutenant Franklin D. Roosevelt, Junior sitting by seaside.
